tika.dc.description: Bounty hunter Iron Eyes had tracked down his prey to an hotel at Rio Concho. He quickly dispatches them and, with the hotel ablaze, drags the bodies outside. But waiting for him is Sheriff Brook Payne and his deputies with rifles trained on him. Iron Eyes is charged with murder and thrown in jail to be tried as soon as Judge Franklin Travis, better known as the Hanging Judge, arrives in town. Can Iron Eyes escape the noose?
